data.description: Beautiful 7+acre farm in The Preserve at Oak Hill. Fenced into 3 pastures and featuring a 6 stall barn, The farm features a 4 bed room 2 bath split bedroom floor plan. The guest bedrooms can form a mother in law suite. Tile flooring stainless appliances and granite counter tops complement the home. A huge screen enclosed  concrete patio makes entertaining easy. The home has a side entry 3 car garage. Come enjoy this equine community complete w/riding trails.
